=== QUESTION TEXT ===
Alizarin yellow R is an azo dye that changes color from yellow to red between pH 10.2 and 12.2. Provide a synthesis of alizarin yellow R from aniline, salicylic acid (o-hydroxybenzoic acid), and any other reagents. Aniline is Nc1ccccc1, salycilic acid is O=C(O)c1ccccc1O, alizarin yellow R is O=C(O)c2cc(N=Nc1ccc(N(=O)=O)cc1)ccc2O. 

